<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- twạḍʿy nfsy .. tḥt yd ạllh
 tḥt yd ạllh .. twạḍʿy nfsy
 1- (fy lylk ạlḥạlk .. fy dẖlẗ ḥạlk
 fy kl ạ̉ḥwạlk .. twạḍʿy nfsy)2
 2- (fy ywmk ạlbạky .. fy wsṭ blwạki
 ky ykẖzy̱ ạ̉ʿdạki .. twạḍʿy nfsy)2
 3- (ạlạ̉mr llạ̹lh fạrḍy .. bmạ yrḍạh
 tʿynk ymnạh .. twạḍʿy nfsy)2
 4- (bḥkmẗ yʿml .. wdẖạ hw ạlạ̉fḍl
 lḥkmh ạlạ̉mtẖl .. twạḍʿy nfsy)2
 5- (kfy ʿn ạlsẖkwy̱ .. mhmạ tkn ạlblwy̱
 fy sẖkẖṣh ạlslwy̱ .. twạḍʿy nfsy)2</lyrics>
<title>twạḍʿy nfsy</title>
<author>zkryạ ʿwḍ ạllh, fwạz ʿmysẖ</author>
